		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://spectrum.ge/images/Projects/Restaurant-Kalaki/KAL4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;At the outset of every project, we identify a procurement methodology that suits your project and reflects the unique characteristics of your project.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We then provide a Procurement Strategy Plan that will ensure a successful completion outcome.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Procurement Tracker&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The procurement tracker is a specially made tool that enables project stakeholders to obtain accurate and online access to all procurement activities such as tender issuance, tender receipts, contract placement, shipment notifications, custom notices and on-site product delivery.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Careful procurement planning is an important factor for maintaining satisfactory results in compliance with the project delivery to its actual form and preventing delays arising from lack of materials or equipment delivered to the construction site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;Procurement&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt; Capabilities Include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
